  "detailed_description": "- Dive into 12 complete story chapters <br>- Choose from 3 difficulty levels, with a minimum of 30 hours experience of main storyline.<br>- Master 4 distinct weapon systems: spears, bows and arrows, swords, and steeds, supplemented by equipment systems like crafting, sets, refinement, and enchantment.<br>- Explore no fewer than 30 expansive maps.<br>- Encounter dozens of well-known Chinese historical figures, who will either fight by your side or become your adversaries.<br>- Enjoy a wide range of visually striking outfits for the protagonist and companions.<br>- Engage in several large-scale, renowned battles that truly capture the essence of the Three Kingdoms atmosphere.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201710/extras/ae841e43185e4c24f491710b2c0e8fe9.poster.avif?t=1731049555\" width=594 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201710/extras/ae841e43185e4c24f491710b2c0e8fe9.webm?t=1731049555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201710/extras/ae841e43185e4c24f491710b2c0e8fe9.mp4?t=1731049555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201710/extras/3c9f21f16ce7c5073204b146c3a7c80b.poster.avif?t=1731049555\" width=594 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201710/extras/3c9f21f16ce7c5073204b146c3a7c80b.webm?t=1731049555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201710/extras/3c9f21f16ce7c5073204b146c3a7c80b.mp4?t=1731049555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><v